data.description: Have you been looking for an affordable house with acreage in the Burleson-Mansfield area, or a place to build some sweat equity? This may be your solution! Multigenerational floor plan with 2-Primary Bedrooms or 1-Primary Bedroom and 1-Office Suite, you choose. 4-Bedrooms, 3-Full Bathrooms, 1-Living, 1-Formal Living, 1-Breakfast Room, and 1-Formal Dining Room with a 24x40 Shop nestled in a desirable quiet area of Rendon. Bring your ideas, livestock, RVs, and toys! All rooms are oversized in addition to having a desirable layout for entertaining. The asking price takes into consideration, the needed updates to the house. Buyers to verify all information contained herein, including but not limited to schools, and measurements.
